{
  "stem": "21308.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And our intelligence officer said, you know, he's a pretty decent chap, and he offered me dinner.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's the little things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyway, I fell and broke my braces.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had get some braces to hitch my trousers up, and I said to one of my signalers, go and find me a pair of braces, Amos.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he came back with the strongest pair of braces-- this is a little digression-- he came back with the strongest pair of braces I have ever seen, and not without cause, the name on them was Herkules, spelled with a K.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I said, these look good, Amos.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, yeah, I don't say the poor old bastard will need any more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said to him, why is that?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, he's dead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said, well, that's a bit rough justice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All I asked for was a pair of braces.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, I was quite pleased when he told me that he was already dead.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He'd been killed in the shell fire.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so anyway, I-- I took his braces.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had needed them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we broke out of there, and we went right across to the Baltic at Lubeck.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we got to Lubeck, and of course, it was absolute chaos.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The German army was trying to surrender, marching down the road in formations.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No arms, mind you, all ready to capitulate, but of course, we had to go up to the Baltic.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we got to the Baltic, and we sealed off the [INAUDIBLE] peninsula, and that was why we had to get there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We wanted-- the powers that be, Churchill or somebody-- wanted that closed off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "From whom I'll leave it to your imagination.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had an interesting time in Lubeck.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
